name: MultiplicationTables

”Alexa, ask times tables what the multiples of 5 are.”
”Alexa, ask times tables for the multiples of twelve.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: times tables
des: This application helps young kids memorize multiplication tables using Alexa. Ask Alexa about any set of multiplication tables from one to twenty and she will recite them slowly and steadily so that they are easy to memorize. This skill will help you as many times as you need as long as you keep on asking!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
